Sample data for Tessera vignettes

Source: R/data.R
tessera_warmup.Rd

Subset of MERFISH lung cancer dataset (Chen et al 2024).

Usage

tessera_warmup

Format

counts and meta data table for 3177 cells.

counts

dgCMatrix of gene-by-cell counts

meta_data

data.frame with spatial locations (XY) and cell lineage (type)

Source

Chen, J.H., Nieman, L.T., Spurrell, M. et al. Human lung cancer harbors spatially organized stem-immunity hubs associated with response to immunotherapy. Nat Immunol 25, 644–658 (2024). https://doi.org/10.1038/s41590-024-01792-2
